reviewText: I have all the EW Seminar VHS, and upgraded them to DVD. It's a great study and every one of the speakers does a great job. Would recommend to any woman wanting to grow in her faith and life.

I can not believe that there are not any reviews on this item?????? I came across this item and it is awesome! This has good quality and a sound message that I think everyone should hear.. I don't want to spoil the view for someone who wants to view this item. So all I will say is that I have viewed this item and it is a part of my library... I am so glad that I did not pass this item up as I would have missed out on an important message...

Happy viewing!
